insert  into `templatable_partial_field`(`id`,`templatable_partial_id`,`name`,`type`,`value`,`created_at`,`updated_at`,`deleted_at`,`key`,`container_attributes`) values (1,1,'content','','<p>Sysflow&trade; Base is the core hub that your complete business management solution runs from. It uses&nbsp;bolt-on, mix and match modules and allows you to manage everything from your website to job&nbsp;quotes,&nbsp;offsite projects&nbsp;to HR, vehicle maintenance to payroll - all&nbsp;in one central&nbsp;place.</p><p>Sysflow&nbsp;is designed for staggered deployment at a rate that suits your business, to minimise business disruption and allow staff time to learn one new system before introducing further developments.</p><p>Security and essential fix updates are automatically deployed to the base platform modules as soon as they become available, to ensure that your system is as secure as possible at all times.</p><p>      </p><p>Sysflow&trade; Base consists of a number of core modules which provides an initial level of functionality, from which you can then build upon.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><a href=\"/roles-module\">Roles</a> - define the level of access by individual,&nbsp;seniority, department or a custom combination choice</li><li><a href=\"/users-module\">Users</a> - assign each employee pre-defined permissions</li><li><a href=\"/styling-module\">Styling</a> - a&nbsp;developer tool to apply branding elements to your system</li><li><a href=\"/contact-manager-module\">Contact Manager</a> - manage customers, suppliers and internal customer profiles</li></ul>','2014-12-24 14:01:20','2014-12-24 14:01:20',NULL,'',''),(2,2,'content','','<p>\r\n	We recognise that every business is&nbsp;different and one size does not fit all. Our packages are designed to be&nbsp;flexible to suit your specific&nbsp;business&nbsp;needs and&nbsp;range from standard websites through to complete workflow platforms.&nbsp;</p><p>Our website content management system (CMS) is designed specifically for&nbsp;use by non-developers, so its easy for everyone to use and absolutely&nbsp;no coding knowledge&nbsp;is necessary.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sysflow Standard Website</strong></p><p>Entry level website with a&nbsp;selection of&nbsp;website modules (such as Pages and Contact Form) which is easily&nbsp;administered through the CMS.</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;\">Hybrid&nbsp;CMS</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>A combination package, facilitating&nbsp;business workflow (with&nbsp;modules  such as Tasks or Jobs)&nbsp;together with&nbsp;your public-facing&nbsp;website.</p><p></p><p></p><p>Sell products online and accept online payments from all major providers</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Business Software Application\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Quote Engines\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Project Management Software\r\n</p>','2014-12-24 14:01:56','2014-12-24 14:01:56',NULL,'',''),(3,3,'content','','<p>We are currently developing a number of different modules&nbsp;</p>','2014-12-24 14:02:17','2014-12-24 14:02:17',NULL,'',''),(4,4,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:02:36','2014-12-24 14:02:36',NULL,'',''),(5,5,'content','','<p>Sysflow Base is the foundation on which each website is built and provides the robust framework for deployment and update of any number of modules. </p><p>  </p><p>Based on a monthly subscription model, Sysflow Base includes a number of core modules, together with security and development upgrades and hosting on our secure servers. &nbsp;</p>','2014-12-24 14:02:54','2014-12-24 14:02:54',NULL,'',''),(6,6,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:03:11','2014-12-24 14:03:11',NULL,'',''),(7,7,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:03:40','2014-12-24 14:03:40',NULL,'',''),(8,8,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:03:51','2014-12-24 14:03:51',NULL,'',''),(9,9,'content','','<p>Sysflow helped us when we were finding it hard to find the time to complete our own website internally. They quickly picked up the designs and ideas we had and buil