 12:46:08','2015-02-10 12:46:08',NULL,'',''),(603,401,'content','','<p>\r\n	<img src=\"https://www.sysflow.co.uk/uploads/tmp/ex3ceh54d9f4919481f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"float: right; margin: 0px 0px 10px 10px;\">\r\n	An integrated workflow platform, delivering control of every aspect of your business from within one central system. A versatile web-based solution, offering a mix and match suite of bolt-on \r\n	<a href=\"https://www.sysflow.co.uk/modules\">modules</a> to streamline and future-proof the day-to-day running of your business.&nbsp;Manage everything from your website to job quotes, offsite projects to HR, vehicle maintenance to payroll - all in one central place.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Scalable to fit any size company and accessible from anywhere*, it will revolutionise the way you run your business.\r\n</p>\r\n<h4><a href=\"https://www.sysflow.co.uk/contact-us\" class=\"btn red\">Request A Demo<i class=\"iconmoon arrow-right\"></i></a></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Benefits</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>User Friendly</strong>  no coding experience required, easy to use interface</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Flexible &amp; Scaleable</strong>  install any number of modules as your business grows.&nbsp;Reduce downtime through staged adoption; integrate new modules&nbsp;at a rate that suits your business, timescale and budget</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Improved Efficiency </strong>- elimination duplication of effort and control information sharing across departments</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Centrally located information</strong> - monitor&nbsp;everything from staff holidays to van servicing, performance appraisals to PAT testing and much more</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Aligned system and business objectives -&nbsp;</strong>through mix and match modules</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Accessible anywhere</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;through the Cloud (internet) by anyone*</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Enhanced security</strong> - the system is not based on open source software, reducing the opportunity for malicious attack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	* internet connection required\r\n</p>','2015-02-10 12:46:55','2015-02-10 12:46:55',NULL,'',''),(605,403,'content','','<p>\r\n	<img src=\"https://www.sysflow.co.uk/uploads/tmp/cgxq3u54d9f4ea20eaa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"float: right; margin: 0px 0px 10px 10px;\">\r\n	We have an ever-expanding suite of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sysflow.co.uk/modules\">Modules</a> that we\'re constantly working on, but if there is some more bespoke&nbsp;functionality&nbsp;that you require, unique to your business, we can build it for you.&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Our skilled team of developers thrive on the challenge of building new widgets, so get in&nbsp;touch with us today to discuss your idea and how we can make it work for you.&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4><a href=\"https://www.sysflow.co.uk/contact-us\" class=\"btn red\">Contact Us About Custom Modules<i class=\"iconmoon arrow-right\"></i></a></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>','2015-02-10 12:47:24','2015-02-10 12:47:24',NULL,'',''),(607,405,'content','','<p>\r\n	We recognise that every business is&nbsp;different and one size does not fit all. Our set&nbsp;packages are designed&nbsp;to suit a broad&nbsp;business&nbsp;need right out of the box, but&nbsp;tailored solutions&nbsp;are our speciality and can design them to do anything you need.&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Our website content management system (CMS) is designed for&nbsp;use by non-developers, so its easy for absolutely&nbsp;everyone to use -&nbsp;\r\n	<strong>and no coding knowledge&nbsp;is necessary</strong>.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4><a href=\"https://www.sysflow.co.uk/contact-us\" class=\"btn red\">Contact Us About A Tailored Solution<i class=\"iconmoon arrow-right\"></i></a></h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>','2015-02-10 12:47:55','2015-02-10 12:47:55',NULL,'',''),(609,407,'left_column','','<div class=\"overview-item\">\r\n	<div class=\"row\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-sm-6 col-md-12 col-lg-6\">\r\n			<a href=\"/standard-